ComicInfo.Summary: The final climactic chapter of the first Demonslayer story arc comes to a dramatic end, as Jaclyn discovers that Michael and the demon are one and the same! Jaclyn must now face the hardest decision of her life as she realizes that she is the only one who can destroy the monster her love created. Plus, now that Kristoph's dark plans have been revealed, how does he fit into the picture and what effect will he have on Jaclyn's decision?
ComicInfo.Title: Jaclyn's Tale Part 3
